arChildNodes.szComment: A Cathedral of Light priest kneels alone in town square, covered in blood and preaching to her flock (hidden indoors.)
A witch of Hawezar kneels in the mud of her local town, beseeching the swamp to fight the Helltide.
A crazed vagabond shouts in town square, covered in blood and laughing at the end of the world.
A belligerent druid shouts to his hiding neighbors, goading them to fight the forces of Hell.
A deluded merchant, trying to convince his neighbors (and himself) that everything will be fine.
